			<exercise>
<title>Representation: Energy Bar Chart</title>
<statement>
			  <p>Explain what information the bar graph representation (from the simulation) displays and how it displays this information.</p>
</statement>
<answer>
<lemma xml:id="r_energy-bar-chart">
	<title>Energy Bar Chart</title>
	<statement>
	<p>An energy bar chart is a graphical representation where each form of energy in a system is represented by a vertical bar.  It is often common to draw a different bar chart for each instant of interest.</p>
	</statement>
	</lemma>
</answer>
